						               													<description>The Goblin Mage is a new Catacomb Lord for Catacombs (Third Edition) that has the ability to summon clones of himself. Choose which clone (blue, purple, or green) is placed during the setup phase.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Features two variations of the Stromm Catacomb Lord, with the second version intended for more experienced players. There is also a monster version corresponding room card where he is featured.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The summon Stromm shot is like a normal summon shot except it allows the overseer to summon up to two additional clones. All clones in play share Stromm's collective pool of remaining health points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each clone takes his own turn, performing one of the shot sequences listed on the rules card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When damaged is inflicted on a clone, the piece is returned to the Overseer and Stromm's health track is reduced by the amount of damage inflicted. A minimum of one clone must remain in play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Clones may be summoned repeatedly during the battle phase. Once Stromm's health track is reduced to 0, all his clones are defeated.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Available as part of the 2020 Dice Tower Kickstarter Builders Pack.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
